{"tid":599372,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"正義聯盟完美屌打鋼鐵英雄成為DC票房最低作品","createTime":"2018-03-20T10:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T16:48:03.000Z","uid":105567,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dffa96eb007813635fa0824ca2b8939f395060ec","tid":599372,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=26331&amp;catid=35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Fmobile%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D26331%26catid%3D35&d=EIEVgFdsdF8RsgjKnb2qbU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a8f36b3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/mobile/article.aspx?id=26331&amp;catid=35</a><br />\n<br />\n《正義聯盟》票房成績唔理想，到依家全球正式結束上映，成績表始終都要公開，該電影成為DCEU目前為止票房最低嘅作品。<br />\n《正義聯盟》集合多位經典英雄登上大銀幕，華納原本對電影嘅期望甚高，可惜11月首周開畫時不但未能打破其他DCEU電影嘅往績，更成為系列嘅包尾大幡。埋單計數，《正義聯盟》全球票房為6.579億美元，比之前排等尾嘅《超人：鋼鐵英雄》（6.68億美元）僅輸1,010萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n現時《蝙蝠俠對超人》居於首位，坐收8.736億美元；緊隨其後有收8.218億美元嘅《神奇女俠》；而《自殺特攻》收7.468億美元排名第三。<br />\n資料來源:<a href=\"http://CBR.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCBR.com&d=EIEVgFdsdF8RsgjKnb2qbU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=14028c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">CBR.com</a>"},{"pid":"22eda4fe2b5bee53926cb5c05a13fadae2e63aa8","tid":599372,"uid":18912,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T10:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" c